WEBVTT

00:02:01.700 --> 00:02:02.280
Breathe out.

00:02:03.060 --> 00:02:03.700
Breathe in.

00:02:04.019 --> 00:02:04.319
That's it.

00:02:04.540 --> 00:02:05.060
Breathe out.

00:02:05.260 --> 00:02:05.819
Yang Xiaofang.

00:02:05.980 --> 00:02:06.560
Don't be nervous.

00:02:06.739 --> 00:02:07.560
Follow my rhythm.

00:02:07.739 --> 00:02:08.919
When I say push, you push.

00:02:08.979 --> 00:02:09.419
Okay, okay.

00:02:09.419 --> 00:02:10.120
Come on, breathe in.

00:02:10.879 --> 00:02:11.340
Breathe in.

00:02:11.599 --> 00:02:12.000
Breathe in.

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:12.800
Breathe out, breathe out.

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:15.280
Do I breathe through my mouth or nose?

00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:16.800
Through your nose, use your nose!

00:02:16.819 --> 00:02:18.360
Out through your mouth. Breathe out.

00:02:27.139 --> 00:02:27.539
Xiaoshu.

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:28.620
Hurry up.

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:30.199
Boss, don't you worry.

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:31.439
Fan Zhu says

00:02:31.439 --> 00:02:32.419
Xiaofang just got to the hospital.

00:02:32.460 --> 00:02:33.539
Giving birth doesn't happen that fast.

00:02:35.060 --> 00:02:36.419
What Master Jia means is,

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:37.639
he says by the timing,

00:02:37.719 --> 00:02:39.139
it's definitely a boy.

00:02:39.800 --> 00:02:41.120
Born on the fifteenth of the eighth month.

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:43.439
The Three Stars shine, bringing fortune and wisdom.

00:02:45.159 --> 00:02:45.539
Red envelope.

00:02:45.740 --> 00:02:46.879
Don't worry, it's all prepared.

00:02:46.979 --> 00:02:47.740
Nothing can go wrong.

00:02:48.500 --> 00:02:50.180
Xiaofang was just being stubborn before.

00:02:50.500 --> 00:02:51.639
Once the baby is born,

00:02:51.639 --> 00:02:52.979
with everything landing on her doorstep,

00:02:53.340 --> 00:02:54.159
she'll have to accept it.

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:57.300
This Xiaofang,

00:02:57.460 --> 00:02:59.020
she's just young and hot-headed.

00:02:59.199 --> 00:03:00.620
Hasn't seen much of the world.

00:03:01.080 --> 00:03:02.120
Can barely support herself,

00:03:02.259 --> 00:03:03.759
yet she's still stubbornly holding on.

00:03:05.159 --> 00:03:06.680
Following you is how I came to know

00:03:07.159 --> 00:03:08.280
that reality, you know,

00:03:08.500 --> 00:03:10.000
matters far more than saving face.

00:03:11.180 --> 00:03:11.560
I...

00:03:11.860 --> 00:03:12.620
You've got a death wish!

00:03:13.819 --> 00:03:14.620
Watch your tone.

00:03:14.840 --> 00:03:15.759
My apologies, my apologies.

00:03:15.900 --> 00:03:17.159
Steady but swift, I mean.

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:18.419
Yes, yes, yes.

00:03:18.939 --> 00:03:19.319
Right.

00:03:19.979 --> 00:03:21.219
Steady but swift, steady but swift.

00:03:27.099 --> 00:03:28.240
Eldest Uncle, Xiaoshu.

00:03:28.439 --> 00:03:29.259
What are you doing here?

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:29.939
Has she given birth?

00:03:30.259 --> 00:03:30.939
Boy or girl?

00:03:31.099 --> 00:03:32.120
No news yet.

00:03:32.699 --> 00:03:33.400
No idea what's going on

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:34.219
in there right now.

00:03:34.539 --> 00:03:35.060
Don't be anxious.

00:03:35.080 --> 00:03:36.280
Come, sit, sit, have a seat first.

00:03:36.639 --> 00:03:37.039
Come on.

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:42.960
Xiaofang, I'm here, Xiaofang!

00:03:44.479 --> 00:03:44.979
Xiaofang!

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.000
What are you shouting for?

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:48.580
It's not like you can give birth for her.

00:03:48.860 --> 00:03:49.439
Wait quietly.

00:03:52.219 --> 00:03:52.699
Aunt.

00:03:53.180 --> 00:03:54.340
Xiao... Xiaofang.

00:03:54.740 --> 00:03:55.680
She's been in there so long,

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:56.759
she'll be alright, right?

00:03:57.259 --> 00:03:58.379
What good does panicking do?

00:03:59.199 --> 00:04:00.120
Sit there and wait.

00:04:40.939 --> 00:04:41.339
Ma

00:04:41.379 --> 00:04:41.800
Ma

00:04:41.860 --> 00:04:42.899
You're all here

00:04:43.699 --> 00:04:44.899
You drove here?

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:47.240
So cool!

00:04:47.579 --> 00:04:48.639
How's Xiaofang doing?

00:04:58.639 --> 00:04:59.339
She gave birth.

00:05:06.339 --> 00:05:07.800
Congratulations! It's a girl.

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:08.779
Four jin two liang.

00:05:38.019 --> 00:05:39.120
Yang Bite

00:05:42.079 --> 00:05:42.959
Yang Bite

00:06:25.139 --> 00:06:26.360
Our family just had a baby granddaughter!

00:06:26.500 --> 00:06:27.199
Come on, come on!

00:06:27.379 --> 00:06:27.720
Come on, come on!

00:06:27.720 --> 00:06:28.220
Have a celebration egg!

00:06:28.220 --> 00:06:29.399
Have an egg, share the good luck!

00:06:29.399 --> 00:06:30.459
Come on, have a celebration egg!

00:06:31.639 --> 00:06:32.139
Come on, come on!

00:06:32.899 --> 00:06:34.079
Come on, share some good luck!

00:06:34.199 --> 00:06:34.579
Here you go.

00:06:35.060 --> 00:06:35.839
Share some good luck!

00:06:36.459 --> 00:06:36.939
Uncle Yang!

00:06:37.360 --> 00:06:37.620
Here.

00:06:38.160 --> 00:06:39.740
Share the good luck of our granddaughter!

00:06:40.019 --> 00:06:40.560
Good luck!

00:06:40.899 --> 00:06:41.560
Here, two eggs for you.

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:43.220
Why don't you have one too?

00:06:43.579 --> 00:06:44.180
Share the good luck.

00:06:44.259 --> 00:06:44.500
That's right.

00:06:44.600 --> 00:06:45.680
No more being a bad egg from now on.

00:06:48.300 --> 00:06:48.759
Over here.

00:06:51.000 --> 00:06:51.639
You.

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:53.199
Help Xiaofang make up her bed.

00:06:53.319 --> 00:06:54.319
She'll be back any minute now.

00:06:54.839 --> 00:06:56.360
Me? I'm off to buy her a bouquet.

00:06:57.040 --> 00:06:57.519
Wait a second.

00:07:03.560 --> 00:07:04.120
Take a break, will you?

00:07:05.879 --> 00:07:06.300
I'll go.

00:07:15.220 --> 00:07:16.100
Fanyan, come on, come on!

00:07:16.199 --> 00:07:16.639
Fanyan!

00:07:17.199 --> 00:07:18.639
Have a celebration egg, have an egg!

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:19.720
My dear in-laws!

00:07:19.879 --> 00:07:20.579
Come, have a celebration egg.

00:07:20.699 --> 00:07:21.199
Have an egg.

00:07:21.420 --> 00:07:23.339
Share the good luck of our granddaughter.

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:25.040
I-I can't eat this stuff.

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:26.139
My cholesterol's too high.

00:07:26.319 --> 00:07:27.699
No, no problem.

00:07:27.939 --> 00:07:29.160
Look, just hear me out.

00:07:29.279 --> 00:07:30.899
You eat the white, I'll eat the yolk.

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:31.439
Honestly.

00:07:31.600 --> 00:07:33.240
Look how pretty this egg is.

00:07:33.300 --> 00:07:34.740
Share the good luck, we put real effort in.

00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:35.800
Everyone's happy, right?

00:07:36.759 --> 00:07:37.620
Don't be so serious.

00:07:37.879 --> 00:07:39.240
The baby's already born.

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:41.060
Shouldn't our two families

00:07:41.060 --> 00:07:41.660
sit down

00:07:42.459 --> 00:07:43.220
and have a proper talk?

00:07:43.220 --> 00:07:44.060
Yes, yes, yes, right.

00:07:44.079 --> 00:07:44.540
Let's talk.

00:07:45.019 --> 00:07:45.500
All right.

00:07:45.980 --> 00:07:46.620
You all carry on.

00:07:46.620 --> 00:07:47.819
Go on, go lay some eggs.

00:07:50.319 --> 00:07:52.160
Take a look, isn't this egg lovely?

00:07:52.339 --> 00:07:52.879
In-laws.

00:07:52.939 --> 00:07:53.680
No, not in-laws.

00:07:58.220 --> 00:07:58.720
Slow down

00:08:02.720 --> 00:08:03.740
Xiaoshu, just go back

00:08:04.300 --> 00:08:05.139
I'll walk you back

00:08:05.279 --> 00:08:06.160
Don't follow me

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.459
Master, my foot

00:08:10.300 --> 00:08:11.879
Grandson, my foot

00:08:13.180 --> 00:08:15.100
They're all con artists

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:16.279
Qing Cang

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:18.139
What are you doing standing here?

00:08:18.860 --> 00:08:20.160
What a day I've had

00:08:20.339 --> 00:08:21.300
Bumped up a generation again

00:08:23.480 --> 00:08:24.279
Yang Fanzhu

00:08:25.879 --> 00:08:26.839
You think this is easy for me?

00:08:27.279 --> 00:08:28.759
It's not easy, not on a holiday like this

00:08:28.819 --> 00:08:29.420
What a hassle

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:31.120
Here are your eggs, red eggs

00:08:31.180 --> 00:08:31.800
Share the good luck

00:08:32.720 --> 00:08:33.740
Red eggs

00:08:35.080 --> 00:08:36.539
I'm just a fool

00:08:38.000 --> 00:08:39.580
I was waiting for Xiaofang to have a boy

00:08:39.580 --> 00:08:40.320
A boy

00:08:40.480 --> 00:08:41.259
And what happened?

00:08:41.840 --> 00:08:43.000
My life, my future

00:08:43.000 --> 00:08:43.960
Everything is completely ruined.

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:44.840
What am I supposed to do?

00:08:45.019 --> 00:08:46.019
So why are you yelling at me?

00:08:46.039 --> 00:08:47.080
It's got nothing to do with me

00:08:47.700 --> 00:08:49.120
So now it's got nothing to do with you?

00:08:50.220 --> 00:08:51.240
That 50,000 yuan in your account

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:51.940
Where did it come from?

00:08:52.559 --> 00:08:53.600
You were being a loyal buddy, weren't you?

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:54.279
Between brothers

00:08:54.539 --> 00:08:55.240
What brothers?

00:08:55.360 --> 00:08:56.200
What brothers?

00:08:56.620 --> 00:08:57.960
Do you know how much I make a month?

00:08:57.960 --> 00:08:59.559
I only make 2,000 yuan a month

00:08:59.779 --> 00:09:01.019
And you asked me for 50,000?

00:09:01.019 --> 00:09:01.639
Keep it down

00:09:01.759 --> 00:09:03.620
I'll pay you back, I'll pay you back

00:09:04.320 --> 00:09:05.399
I'll pay you back by New Year

00:09:05.620 --> 00:09:06.360
Pay me back by New Year?

00:09:06.700 --> 00:09:07.240
Why don't you just wait

00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:08.179
till the kid goes to college to pay me?

00:09:09.580 --> 00:09:10.159
Pay me back right now

00:09:10.539 --> 00:09:11.159
I don't have it. Pay up

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:11.639
What are you doing?

00:09:11.740 --> 00:09:12.679
Pay up

00:09:12.679 --> 00:09:13.500
I don't have money

00:09:13.879 --> 00:09:15.299
I don't have money right now, Qing Cang

00:09:15.559 --> 00:09:16.460
I'm broke

00:09:17.019 --> 00:09:17.779
Where's your money?

00:09:18.440 --> 00:09:19.200
I paid off other debts

00:09:22.700 --> 00:09:24.059
That was my money

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:27.000
Aren't you the loyal one.

00:09:27.879 --> 00:09:30.019
Using my money to pay off your debts.

00:09:31.279 --> 00:09:33.639
You're all good people

00:09:34.820 --> 00:09:36.919
I'm the only bad egg.

00:09:38.899 --> 00:09:41.299
I don't want to be a bad egg.

00:09:43.879 --> 00:09:46.120
I want to turn things around

00:09:53.299 --> 00:09:56.000
I never hurt anyone

00:09:57.960 --> 00:09:59.620
Why me?

00:10:10.120 --> 00:10:12.120
Give me back my money!

00:10:13.159 --> 00:10:13.840
Qing Cang, back at my place,

00:10:15.000 --> 00:10:16.240
I've still got a bunch of lottery tickets.

00:10:16.379 --> 00:10:17.820
I'll definitely win your money back.

00:10:20.799 --> 00:10:22.279
I've got great luck.

00:10:23.279 --> 00:10:24.600
I ate the red eggs too.

00:10:25.039 --> 00:10:25.940
Shared in the good luck.

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.139
Just you watch this time.

00:10:30.940 --> 00:10:31.580
Qing Cang.

00:10:32.259 --> 00:10:37.360
He even used my money to buy scratch cards!

00:10:38.220 --> 00:10:38.980
Have an egg.

00:10:40.679 --> 00:10:41.279
Don't cry.

00:10:42.659 --> 00:10:43.340
This is a public place.

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:56.700
We agreed

00:10:56.720 --> 00:10:58.200
Whatever I win on these scratch cards is all mine

00:10:59.519 --> 00:11:01.039
Today it's for Bite, tomorrow it's yours

00:11:02.080 --> 00:11:03.139
Why should it be?

00:11:03.299 --> 00:11:04.500
Yang Bite never borrowed money from you

00:11:04.679 --> 00:11:06.600
It's just for the kid's good luck, that's all

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:07.639
You didn't even give a gift today

00:11:07.659 --> 00:11:08.340
Perfect timing

00:11:08.580 --> 00:11:09.559
I still have to give a gift

00:11:09.559 --> 00:11:10.340
And I've still got to give to you Yangs

00:11:10.340 --> 00:11:11.159
How much am I supposed to spend?

00:11:11.200 --> 00:11:12.179
Alright, alright, you...

00:11:12.639 --> 00:11:13.200
Did you win anything?

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:14.059
Twenty

00:11:14.240 --> 00:11:15.000
Just broke even

00:11:15.960 --> 00:11:16.639
Just now on my end

00:11:16.700 --> 00:11:17.580
I hit a fifty

00:11:18.059 --> 00:11:18.779
That's what breaking even looks like

00:11:20.059 --> 00:11:20.580
Boss

00:11:20.600 --> 00:11:22.019
I'll just transfer it to you directly

00:11:22.139 --> 00:11:23.200
Thanks for your business

00:11:23.440 --> 00:11:24.080
Here's your bouquet

00:11:24.379 --> 00:11:24.879
Thank you

00:11:25.159 --> 00:11:25.960
Happy holidays

00:11:26.200 --> 00:11:27.139
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:29.440
Bro, this millet porridge is too plain

00:11:29.500 --> 00:11:30.759
It's not appetizing at all

00:11:31.279 --> 00:11:32.799
Are you the one eating it, or her?

00:11:33.500 --> 00:11:34.379
I think this one's better

00:11:34.379 --> 00:11:35.360
Look, five-red porridge

00:11:35.580 --> 00:11:36.700
It replenishes blood and energy

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:37.480
No, no, no

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:38.919
This one here

00:11:38.960 --> 00:11:40.379
It's got peanuts and red beans

00:11:40.460 --> 00:11:41.340
Those cause bloating easily

00:11:41.580 --> 00:11:42.679
She just gave birth

00:11:43.080 --> 00:11:44.519
You even know all this?

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:46.759
Stop bugging your eyes out at me.

00:11:47.039 --> 00:11:49.039
If I don't know, I can learn

00:11:50.039 --> 00:11:51.000
If my old man Qian

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:52.379
were even half as good as you, that'd be great

00:11:53.679 --> 00:11:55.240
You're a model dad, really

00:11:56.519 --> 00:11:57.460
Bro, you're so sweet

00:11:58.279 --> 00:11:59.120
I'll take all of them

00:11:59.480 --> 00:12:00.679
Family of Yang Xiaofang

00:12:03.100 --> 00:12:04.299
Family of Yang Xiaofang

00:12:04.879 --> 00:12:05.340
That's me

00:12:07.460 --> 00:12:08.659
You're Yang Xiaofang's family?

00:12:11.960 --> 00:12:13.360
I'm the child's...

00:12:17.620 --> 00:12:18.820
Fa... father

00:12:20.559 --> 00:12:21.279
Sorry, I...

00:12:21.559 --> 00:12:22.200
I've got no strength left

00:12:22.539 --> 00:12:23.019
It's fine

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:26.440
This is the newborn's

00:12:26.500 --> 00:12:27.639
birth condition record form

00:12:27.759 --> 00:12:28.279
Please keep it safe

00:13:00.980 --> 00:13:02.379
I'm a father now

00:13:23.159 --> 00:13:23.759
Grandma

00:13:24.960 --> 00:13:25.799
Where's the baby?

00:13:27.419 --> 00:13:30.000
In the incubator, don't worry.

00:13:30.279 --> 00:13:31.940
Bite is very healthy.

00:13:33.259 --> 00:13:34.639
He's just a little small.

00:13:35.159 --> 00:13:37.379
But he'll catch up soon enough.

00:13:41.480 --> 00:13:43.200
You're all so tight-lipped.

00:13:44.100 --> 00:13:45.360
Nobody even told me

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:46.820
that giving birth hurts so much!

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:50.059
My whole body feels like it fell apart

00:13:50.059 --> 00:13:51.279
and got put back together.

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:54.179
Before I even got the chance to tell you,

00:13:54.500 --> 00:13:55.740
you were already pregnant.

00:13:56.340 --> 00:13:58.120
Before I even got the chance to tell you,

00:13:58.460 --> 00:14:00.019
you'd already given birth.

00:14:08.019 --> 00:14:08.639
Grandma,

00:14:10.500 --> 00:14:12.240
you had four kids.

00:14:13.399 --> 00:14:15.279
Did every one of them hurt this much?

00:14:16.580 --> 00:14:17.820
Every single one hurt.

00:14:20.559 --> 00:14:21.440
But you know,

00:14:22.279 --> 00:14:24.379
the moment you see your baby,

00:14:25.299 --> 00:14:27.840
a voice inside just tells you,

00:14:29.820 --> 00:14:30.500
Done!

00:14:42.779 --> 00:14:43.899
No way, no way, end of discussion.

00:14:43.960 --> 00:14:45.360
Fanyan, it's settled then.

00:14:45.419 --> 00:14:46.879
She'll do her postpartum confinement at our place.

00:14:46.940 --> 00:14:47.980
We promise to take good care of Xiaofang.

00:14:48.019 --> 00:14:49.139
Don't flatter yourself.

00:14:49.259 --> 00:14:49.919
Just get over yourself.

00:14:50.179 --> 00:14:50.480
Hold on.

00:14:50.740 --> 00:14:52.200
What do you mean, flatter myself?

00:14:52.240 --> 00:14:52.820
Yeah, we're proud of ourselves.

00:14:52.860 --> 00:14:54.000
We dare to dream and dare to do.

00:15:03.039 --> 00:15:03.539
Take care now.

00:15:03.820 --> 00:15:04.440
Come again sometime.

00:15:04.440 --> 00:15:04.980
Bro.

00:15:05.460 --> 00:15:06.220
Fireworks!

00:15:07.940 --> 00:15:08.539
Fireworks!

00:15:11.320 --> 00:15:12.139
So clueless.

00:15:13.740 --> 00:15:14.720
Quick, quick, quick, come on!

00:15:18.340 --> 00:15:19.419
So beautiful!

00:15:23.940 --> 00:15:27.059
Whether you're a mom or not,

00:15:27.860 --> 00:15:28.879
life, you know,

00:15:30.159 --> 00:15:31.919
should be just like these fireworks,

00:15:33.320 --> 00:15:34.500
lived brilliantly.

00:16:14.820 --> 00:16:15.519
Done!

00:16:17.620 --> 00:16:18.639
Nicely done!

00:16:21.759 --> 00:16:24.200
Jingjing, happy Mid-Autumn Festival!

00:16:25.259 --> 00:16:26.700
Can I have a candied hawthorn stick

00:16:26.700 --> 00:16:27.740
as a gift?

00:16:29.580 --> 00:16:31.080
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival!

00:16:31.899 --> 00:16:33.019
Happy Mid-Autumn!

00:16:33.820 --> 00:16:34.879
All this time,

00:16:35.360 --> 00:16:36.460
thanks to you and Fanyan.

00:16:38.240 --> 00:16:38.700
Bro.

00:16:39.539 --> 00:16:40.240
Happy Mid-Autumn!

00:16:41.279 --> 00:16:41.919
My eldest granddaughter.

00:16:42.639 --> 00:16:44.039
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival!

00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:45.879
Happy Mid-Autumn!

00:16:47.600 --> 00:16:48.279
Happy Mid-Autumn!

00:16:52.460 --> 00:16:53.399
Happy Mid-Autumn!

00:16:53.700 --> 00:16:54.940
Now you're doing it on purpose!

00:17:00.679 --> 00:17:01.519
Grandma.

00:17:03.399 --> 00:17:04.880
Happy Mid-Autumn!

00:17:09.700 --> 00:17:10.839
Happy Mid-Autumn!

00:17:17.839 --> 00:17:18.619
Happy Mid-Autumn!

00:17:34.400 --> 00:17:34.900
Fan Mei

00:17:35.039 --> 00:17:35.500
You're back

00:17:35.700 --> 00:17:36.460
Yeah, I'm back

00:17:37.019 --> 00:17:37.380
Ma

00:17:39.880 --> 00:17:40.680
Grab one of the eggs

00:17:41.960 --> 00:17:42.619
Me? Me? Me?

00:17:42.660 --> 00:17:43.319
Then I won't take one for now

00:17:43.319 --> 00:17:43.900
My bag

00:17:45.200 --> 00:17:45.619
Right

00:17:53.000 --> 00:17:53.500
So small

00:18:03.519 --> 00:18:04.000
Old Qi!

00:18:04.099 --> 00:18:04.480
Come here, come here!

00:18:04.480 --> 00:18:05.000
You look bright and cheery today!

00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:06.180
Here, have some red eggs, some red eggs!

00:18:06.240 --> 00:18:07.259
Our granddaughter's home!

00:18:08.000 --> 00:18:09.440
So Xiaofang and Xiaowei made up, huh?

00:18:09.500 --> 00:18:10.000
Congratulations, congratulations!

00:18:10.039 --> 00:18:11.519
Young folks have their little spats.

00:18:12.039 --> 00:18:12.660
They patched it up ages ago.

00:18:13.180 --> 00:18:13.900
And that granddaughter of mine,

00:18:13.960 --> 00:18:15.160
she's such a pretty little thing!

00:18:15.640 --> 00:18:17.079
Uncle Qi, Uncle Qi.

00:18:17.299 --> 00:18:18.279
A granddaughter's all well and good,

00:18:18.579 --> 00:18:19.759
but why didn't Xiaofang give you

00:18:19.759 --> 00:18:20.700
a fine grandson instead?

00:18:21.619 --> 00:18:23.420
I've had my fill of raising sons!

00:18:23.500 --> 00:18:23.880
That's right.

00:18:23.920 --> 00:18:24.700
Sons are nothing but debt.

00:18:25.859 --> 00:18:26.279
Let me tell you,

00:18:26.299 --> 00:18:26.799
after all this trouble,

00:18:26.819 --> 00:18:27.640
I finally got a granddaughter!

00:18:28.079 --> 00:18:29.359
Come to the one-month party when it's time!

00:18:29.400 --> 00:18:29.740
Will do!

00:18:30.119 --> 00:18:30.940
Thank you! Congratulations!

00:18:30.980 --> 00:18:31.380
Sure, sure, sure!

00:18:31.380 --> 00:18:31.799
Old Qi.

00:18:32.160 --> 00:18:32.619
Old Qi.

00:18:32.960 --> 00:18:34.440
Looks like the one-month party and the wedding

00:18:34.440 --> 00:18:35.259
will be one big celebration, huh?

00:18:35.599 --> 00:18:36.220
Well, uh...

00:18:36.460 --> 00:18:37.960
Our Xiaofang hasn't agreed to it.

00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:39.119
Is this really a good idea?

00:18:39.339 --> 00:18:40.799
What's there to fear? The baby's born!

00:18:41.220 --> 00:18:41.960
The whole village knows

00:18:41.960 --> 00:18:42.920
it's the Qi family's blood.

00:18:43.119 --> 00:18:44.099
This is called breaking news.

00:18:44.180 --> 00:18:44.980
Get the word out first,

00:18:45.279 --> 00:18:46.039
and the Yang family won't have a say.

00:18:46.079 --> 00:18:47.440
Come on, let's head to the Yang place.

00:18:47.579 --> 00:18:49.240
Alright, alright, let's go, let's go!

00:18:49.259 --> 00:18:50.720
Give us a heads-up when the time comes!

00:18:51.720 --> 00:18:52.259
You bet!

00:19:07.940 --> 00:19:09.400
What... what do you think you're doing?

00:19:09.779 --> 00:19:11.000
What are you doing?

00:19:11.759 --> 00:19:13.319
You rotten scoundrel!

00:19:13.559 --> 00:19:14.799
Our Yang Bite just fell asleep

00:19:14.819 --> 00:19:15.619
and you set off firecrackers

00:19:16.059 --> 00:19:16.819
scaring the baby!

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:18.819
I'll make sure you never sleep well again!

00:19:19.559 --> 00:19:20.559
I was just celebrating!

00:19:20.759 --> 00:19:21.839
I didn't mean to scare the baby

00:19:22.819 --> 00:19:23.859
My family had the baby,

00:19:23.859 --> 00:19:25.039
so what have you got to celebrate?

00:19:27.480 --> 00:19:28.740
You're even handing out red eggs

00:19:29.599 --> 00:19:30.700
What, Bie Qiumei,

00:19:31.220 --> 00:19:32.500
answering the nation's call,

00:19:32.839 --> 00:19:33.759
you got pregnant again?

00:19:38.799 --> 00:19:39.759
Back at my place,

00:19:39.779 --> 00:19:41.240
I've got chicken soup stewing for Xiaofang

00:19:41.539 --> 00:19:42.420
I'm heading back now

00:19:43.740 --> 00:19:44.380
Why is she leaving?

00:19:44.759 --> 00:19:45.720
Yang Fan Mei,

00:19:46.319 --> 00:19:47.799
you've lived in the big city too

00:19:48.220 --> 00:19:49.420
Can't you show a little class?

00:19:49.619 --> 00:19:50.480
Don't just curse at every turn

00:19:50.599 --> 00:19:51.960
After all, our families are in-laws

00:19:52.359 --> 00:19:53.140
In-laws?

00:19:53.539 --> 00:19:55.140
More like enemies living across the way

00:19:55.740 --> 00:19:56.279
Get lost, now!

00:19:56.619 --> 00:19:57.380
Don't let me see your face!

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:03.599
Fan Mei!

00:20:04.279 --> 00:20:04.880
You... you... you...

00:20:04.980 --> 00:20:06.119
What kind of water did you just throw?

00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:06.680
This smell...

00:20:07.339 --> 00:20:08.819
Water from washing Yang Bite's butt.

00:20:11.700 --> 00:20:12.380
I'm honored!

00:20:12.740 --> 00:20:13.680
This I can accept

00:20:14.619 --> 00:20:14.980
Retreat!

00:20:15.299 --> 00:20:16.759
Okay, okay, let's go

00:20:16.859 --> 00:20:19.440
Go, go, go! Go, go, go! Let's go!

00:20:34.440 --> 00:20:36.099
Why is she always sleeping?

00:20:36.539 --> 00:20:38.279
When will she wake up and play with me?

00:20:39.259 --> 00:20:41.140
Kids are angels when they're asleep.

00:20:41.460 --> 00:20:42.720
And demons when they're awake.

00:20:43.019 --> 00:20:44.279
If you want to play, now's the time.

00:20:45.299 --> 00:20:46.279
That's no fun.

00:20:47.140 --> 00:20:48.519
I want to hear her call me Uncle.

00:20:51.920 --> 00:20:52.420
Dandan.

00:20:52.740 --> 00:20:54.400
Wanting to be an uncle already, huh?

00:20:55.019 --> 00:20:56.839
Here, have some eggs. I made them for you.

00:20:57.380 --> 00:20:57.720
Aunt.

00:20:57.980 --> 00:20:59.259
I just had two bowls of soup.

00:20:59.279 --> 00:21:00.180
I'm really pretty full.

00:21:00.559 --> 00:21:02.019
These are fried in camellia oil.

00:21:02.059 --> 00:21:03.119
A folk remedy to boost milk supply.

00:21:03.200 --> 00:21:03.480
Come on.

00:21:03.660 --> 00:21:04.240
If it really doesn't work,

00:21:04.279 --> 00:21:05.299
just give Bite formula, I mean.

00:21:06.900 --> 00:21:07.640
Don't be silly.

00:21:08.000 --> 00:21:08.799
Let me tell you something.

00:21:09.299 --> 00:21:10.400
I'll leave this here for you to eat later.

00:21:11.599 --> 00:21:12.579
Jingjing, you know,

00:21:13.000 --> 00:21:14.579
when she was little, it was because

00:21:14.779 --> 00:21:16.140
she didn't get enough breast milk.

00:21:16.819 --> 00:21:17.940
And so from a young age,

00:21:18.019 --> 00:21:19.339
she was always getting sick.

00:21:19.779 --> 00:21:20.440
Formula,

00:21:20.759 --> 00:21:22.559
how could it ever compare to breast milk?

00:21:23.059 --> 00:21:24.079
But I looked it up.

00:21:24.119 --> 00:21:25.119
These days, formula

00:21:25.180 --> 00:21:26.839
is just as nutritious as breast milk.

00:21:27.400 --> 00:21:29.019
That's a hidden ad.

00:21:29.460 --> 00:21:30.059
Don't believe it.

00:21:32.680 --> 00:21:34.099
I've got two more soups too.

00:21:34.660 --> 00:21:35.859
Pigeon soup and fish soup.

00:21:36.559 --> 00:21:37.460
You've got to finish them all.

00:21:37.779 --> 00:21:38.319
Don't you worry.

00:21:38.519 --> 00:21:39.440
In just a few days,

00:21:39.900 --> 00:21:40.619
your milk will be flowing

00:21:40.920 --> 00:21:42.160
just like Niagara Falls.

00:21:42.160 --> 00:21:43.799
I've already had so many bowls today.

00:21:44.119 --> 00:21:45.720
Don't taste it! No sneaking bites!

00:21:56.460 --> 00:21:57.240
You want some?

00:22:00.019 --> 00:22:01.299
I'm still growing, you know.

00:22:01.559 --> 00:22:02.460
I can eat as much as you've got.

00:22:06.980 --> 00:22:07.640
It's all yours.

00:22:07.819 --> 00:22:08.480
Come on, eat up.

00:22:09.339 --> 00:22:09.660
Here.

00:22:15.519 --> 00:22:16.160
This tastes awful.

00:22:16.680 --> 00:22:17.480
There's no salt in it, is there?

00:22:17.759 --> 00:22:18.619
It's completely bland.

00:22:19.220 --> 00:22:20.460
Why are they making you eat this?

00:22:20.660 --> 00:22:21.559
It boosts my milk supply.

00:22:32.740 --> 00:22:34.680
Aren't these diapers supposed to be leak-proof?

00:22:36.119 --> 00:22:37.759
How did she manage to leak this much?

00:22:39.700 --> 00:22:40.519
I'll wash it, I'll wash it.

00:22:41.539 --> 00:22:42.720
Uncle, go take a rest.

00:22:46.099 --> 00:22:46.519
Hold on.

00:22:46.839 --> 00:22:47.680
You're being nice, so you're up to no good.

00:22:47.680 --> 00:22:48.339
I'd better do it myself.

00:22:50.779 --> 00:22:51.859
How could you think that of me?

00:22:52.119 --> 00:22:53.220
These are my daughter's clothes.

00:22:53.420 --> 00:22:54.359
If I don't wash them, who will?

00:22:54.539 --> 00:22:55.059
Am I right?

00:22:55.160 --> 00:22:56.319
Whatever chores you've got, just tell me.

00:22:56.319 --> 00:22:57.079
I can handle them all.

00:23:01.039 --> 00:23:01.599
Xiaowei, I think

00:23:01.599 --> 00:23:02.519
you've got a point.

00:23:03.059 --> 00:23:03.880
You're better at this than me.

00:23:04.400 --> 00:23:05.240
Go on, do a good job.

00:23:05.420 --> 00:23:05.680
Okay.

00:23:08.279 --> 00:23:08.839
Fan Zhu.

00:23:11.240 --> 00:23:11.980
Quick, they're calling you.

00:23:11.980 --> 00:23:13.140
Hurry, big job to do, go, go!

00:23:14.059 --> 00:23:14.740
Fan Zhu.

00:23:16.859 --> 00:23:18.660
So much stuff, is something broken here?

00:23:24.279 --> 00:23:24.980
The roof's broken.

00:23:27.859 --> 00:23:28.539
In-laws.

00:23:31.140 --> 00:23:32.700
On a hot day like this, keeping busy?

00:23:33.319 --> 00:23:33.960
I'll poke you.

00:23:36.240 --> 00:23:36.819
Go on!

00:23:37.099 --> 00:23:37.740
What is it?

00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:39.960
I poked you.

00:23:47.039 --> 00:23:48.839
I stewed some chicken soup for Xiaofang.

00:23:49.299 --> 00:23:50.400
A little black-boned rooster.

00:23:50.559 --> 00:23:51.559
To help build up her strength.

00:23:51.660 --> 00:23:52.279
Let me tell you something.

00:23:52.900 --> 00:23:54.119
Our family doesn't need it.

00:23:56.039 --> 00:23:57.539
Don't be like that, glaring at me.

00:23:57.640 --> 00:23:58.259
What's the matter?

00:23:58.519 --> 00:23:59.480
We're all one family.

00:24:00.579 --> 00:24:01.940
Right, Ma means well.

00:24:01.940 --> 00:24:02.420
Dad.

00:24:02.880 --> 00:24:03.940
Who are you calling Dad?

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:05.299
Who's your dad?

00:24:07.859 --> 00:24:09.180
Uncle, Uncle, Uncle Yang.

00:24:10.279 --> 00:24:11.079
What about Bite, then?

00:24:11.119 --> 00:24:13.259
She's my daughter too, you know.

00:24:20.660 --> 00:24:22.380
Bite's your daughter, huh?

00:24:23.839 --> 00:24:24.680
Xiaofang

00:24:25.380 --> 00:24:26.460
is my daughter.

00:24:27.500 --> 00:24:28.160
Bite

00:24:29.039 --> 00:24:30.099
is my granddaughter.

00:24:31.019 --> 00:24:32.119
People from our family

00:24:32.259 --> 00:24:33.259
and people from your family

00:24:33.259 --> 00:24:34.579
on the same household register.

00:24:35.440 --> 00:24:36.259
Disgusting.

00:24:37.539 --> 00:24:38.140
Huzi.

00:24:38.160 --> 00:24:39.240
What are you doing, talking like that?

00:24:39.319 --> 00:24:40.079
Xiaowei, hurry up.

00:24:40.079 --> 00:24:40.640
This, this, this...

00:24:41.140 --> 00:24:42.160
Go, go, go, get on it.

00:24:44.460 --> 00:24:44.960
Huzi, Huzi.

00:24:45.220 --> 00:24:45.940
Xiaofang.

00:24:46.059 --> 00:24:47.460
Auntie stewed some chicken soup for you.

00:24:47.579 --> 00:24:49.279
Drink it up quick.

00:24:49.640 --> 00:24:50.579
Build up your strength.

00:24:54.920 --> 00:24:55.380
Huzi.

00:24:56.059 --> 00:24:57.299
How about I help you with something?

00:25:01.079 --> 00:25:01.980
Help me by

00:25:02.940 --> 00:25:04.140
getting out of here fast.

00:25:10.200 --> 00:25:10.759
Huzi.

00:25:11.160 --> 00:25:12.440
You look really good today.

00:25:12.579 --> 00:25:14.180
Your little eyes are so bright.

00:25:15.400 --> 00:25:16.599
Fortune's smiling on you.

00:25:17.460 --> 00:25:18.220
I'm heading back now.

00:25:18.779 --> 00:25:19.700
Xiaofang.

00:25:19.799 --> 00:25:21.279
Drink the chicken soup, build up your strength.

00:25:21.920 --> 00:25:22.339
Xiaofang.

00:25:25.019 --> 00:25:25.380
Um...

00:25:25.640 --> 00:25:26.680
The chicken soup my ma stewed,

00:25:26.900 --> 00:25:27.420
drink it while it's hot.

00:25:29.920 --> 00:25:31.000
I can't stomach any more chicken soup.

00:25:31.039 --> 00:25:32.619
The smell alone makes me sick.

00:25:32.759 --> 00:25:33.559
It's so disgusting.

00:25:35.460 --> 00:25:36.079
What's wrong?

00:25:37.299 --> 00:25:38.079
I've got no milk.

00:25:38.619 --> 00:25:40.000
They stew all kinds of soup every day.

00:25:40.059 --> 00:25:41.619
Several bowls a day, to boost my milk supply.

00:25:43.920 --> 00:25:44.920
If you don't want it, don't drink it.

00:25:45.200 --> 00:25:45.680
Um...

00:25:46.299 --> 00:25:47.720
No milk? We can just use formula.

00:25:50.420 --> 00:25:51.339
You really think that way?

00:25:53.539 --> 00:25:54.339
What do you feel like eating?

00:25:54.519 --> 00:25:55.319
I'll go buy it for you.

00:25:57.059 --> 00:25:58.119
Hold your daughter first.

00:25:59.819 --> 00:26:00.200
Baby.

00:26:01.000 --> 00:26:02.880
Come, let Mommy hold you, okay?

00:26:03.460 --> 00:26:04.099
Me?

00:26:05.660 --> 00:26:06.400
Who else?

00:26:12.920 --> 00:26:14.619
Put the chicken soup down, how can you hold him?

00:26:14.799 --> 00:26:15.059
Okay

00:26:16.980 --> 00:26:17.880
Baby

00:26:19.339 --> 00:26:20.220
Support his bottom

00:26:23.839 --> 00:26:24.740
Support his neck

00:26:36.160 --> 00:26:37.420
She's so tiny and soft.

00:26:53.799 --> 00:26:54.740
It's okay

00:27:04.559 --> 00:27:05.079
We'll

00:27:05.720 --> 00:27:06.940
grow up little by little

00:27:07.420 --> 00:27:08.759
As long as

00:27:09.240 --> 00:27:11.180
today, compared to yesterday,

00:27:11.359 --> 00:27:13.220
you grow just a tiny bit more,

00:27:13.440 --> 00:27:14.640
weigh just a tiny bit more,

00:27:14.640 --> 00:27:15.940
that's all that matters, right?

00:27:32.920 --> 00:27:33.799
She's asleep.

00:27:40.779 --> 00:27:42.099
Your mom's asleep too.

00:27:44.940 --> 00:27:45.559
She's tired.

00:27:46.099 --> 00:27:47.279
Let's not disturb her.

00:27:58.779 --> 00:27:59.359
So, how is it?

00:28:00.480 --> 00:28:02.220
Getting used to studying here for a while?

00:28:03.119 --> 00:28:04.299
We're not going back to find my dad.

00:28:04.880 --> 00:28:05.640
Why would we?

00:28:06.440 --> 00:28:07.240
He's still dodging his debts.

00:28:08.039 --> 00:28:08.460
Xiaofang.

00:28:09.460 --> 00:28:10.700
The Qi family's soup to boost milk supply

00:28:10.779 --> 00:28:12.799
was delivered right on schedule.

00:28:15.619 --> 00:28:16.299
So greasy,

00:28:16.819 --> 00:28:17.579
full of lymph nodes,

00:28:18.259 --> 00:28:19.599
and herbs to boost milk supply, huh?

00:28:20.539 --> 00:28:22.539
They're terrified the baby might go hungry,

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:24.740
but they don't care about our Xiaofang at all!

00:28:24.980 --> 00:28:26.059
My advice? This soup,

00:28:26.799 --> 00:28:27.579
let's not drink it.

00:28:27.880 --> 00:28:28.859
Things could get complicated later.

00:28:29.640 --> 00:28:30.039
I mean, think about it.

00:28:30.140 --> 00:28:31.500
The moment they heard it's a girl,

00:28:32.079 --> 00:28:33.319
Eldest Uncle and Qing Cang

00:28:33.559 --> 00:28:34.940
vanished without a trace.

00:28:35.519 --> 00:28:37.039
But this Qi Deyao,

00:28:37.559 --> 00:28:39.480
he's running around shouting for joy,

00:28:39.480 --> 00:28:40.039
making a big fuss.

00:28:40.700 --> 00:28:42.599
I bet he's got his eye on little Bite.

00:28:43.079 --> 00:28:44.579
Everyone's got their own scheme.

00:28:45.240 --> 00:28:46.339
Eldest Uncle isn't short of money.

00:28:46.819 --> 00:28:48.039
What he wants is to carry on the family line.

00:28:48.480 --> 00:28:49.599
Once the Qi family has a grandson,

00:28:49.880 --> 00:28:51.200
it's like installing a money pit.

00:28:51.640 --> 00:28:52.680
They're just waiting for our Bite

00:28:52.720 --> 00:28:54.180
to earn his marriage money.

00:28:54.640 --> 00:28:55.619
Ma, don't worry.

00:28:55.619 --> 00:28:57.299
I'll earn my own money to get married.

00:28:57.299 --> 00:28:58.039
You don't need to worry about it.

00:28:59.819 --> 00:29:01.019
Thinking that far ahead already.

00:29:01.980 --> 00:29:03.119
Just now, Bie Qiumei

00:29:03.119 --> 00:29:04.180
gave me a little hint.

00:29:04.720 --> 00:29:05.660
Their family's bride price

00:29:06.099 --> 00:29:07.480
can go up to this much.

00:29:09.039 --> 00:29:09.980
That much?

00:29:11.420 --> 00:29:12.980
And that's just the starting point.

00:29:13.500 --> 00:29:14.240
From the way Bie Qiumei

00:29:14.240 --> 00:29:15.240
was hinting between the lines,

00:29:15.579 --> 00:29:16.480
this price

00:29:16.920 --> 00:29:18.059
could still go higher.

