I'm not Yang Xiaofang anymore.

00:40:37.559 --> 00:40:38.559
I'm a dairy cow.

00:40:40.320 --> 00:40:42.099
A cow that can't even make milk.

00:40:42.699 --> 00:40:43.739
What's wrong with being a cow?

00:40:43.780 --> 00:40:45.039
